'''Segnor's Loop''' was a tactical evasive maneuver in which an attacking [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] makes a quick run away from its target before doubling back for a second pass. [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] used the tactic at least once while pursuing [[Rivo Xarran]].

